Outliers

data2 <- data1

findOutliers <- function(df, cutoff = 3) {
  ## Calculate the sd
  sds <- apply(df, 2, sd, na.rm=T)
  ## Identufy the cell with value greater than cutoff * sd (column wise)
  result <- mapply(function(d, s){
    which(d > cutoff * s)
  }, df, sds)
  result
}

outliers <- findOutliers(data2)
